<br>
To any non-amazon, it would sound just like thier customary tribal music beat.. but this one was scattered around the the village, within the forest around them.  Its tune was darker... and much more violent than any amazon songs.  It was a song of summoning, and death.  Like a signal, or becon.  <br>
<br>
The eyes all looked towards the beating of the drums, and from the trees and into the village roof tops, a dozen saurian spies sprung out.  As if they came alive from the shadows, each one snarled and hissed at the amazons below, snapping their talons and teeth at them.  The turned towards the drums and sprinted from roof to roof, tearing them up in the process with thier dreaded talons.  Several of them run through the streets with amazing speeds...slashing away at anything in thier way, bringing down horses within seconds.<br>
<br>
Each saurian scattered back into the woodworks, leaving behind quite a mess.  Though no amazons were hurt, it's come to realization that they have been spied on by these lizardmen for an unknown amount of time.  As each saurian dissapears from view, the drums begin to stop.  There was a dead silence, and everything was calm.  <br>
<br>
But something stood at the village entrance... a large flag, with a picture of a sun blocked out by a Dark Moon, with 3 slash marks through it... the symbol of Varsith, city of the Saurians... A symbol of war.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> QueenPallas</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(8/23/01 4:33 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Queen Pallas Summons the Goddesses</span><hr size=1> Queen Pallas looked at the flag. Shaking her head, she removed the flag from her villages entrance. With her head bowed in respect, and her arms open, she began chanting to summon the Goddesses. <br>
<br>
Kel to began to join her in the chant, along with the other Amazons of the Sacred Circle. Their powerful voices rang to the high heavens of Mount Olympus. In a shower of powerful radiant light, the Goddesses began to materialize.<br>
<br>
Hera, Athena, Artemis, Hestia, and Demeter stood before the Amazons. Pallas handed Athena the Saurians flag. Athena looked to Hera and shook her head. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START >: --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/mad.gif ALT=">:"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Pallas bowed. &quot;We are not Amazons of War... bless this sacred space for us,&quot; Pallas asked.<br>
<br>
&quot;We will do more than that, you have our undivided protection and blessings. No creature, Amazon, Man, woman, God or child, shall declare war on the Amazons of the Sacred Circle. To do so, would go against the Goddesses of Mount Olympus. You have my word,&quot; Athena said to Pallas.<br>
<br>
Pallas bowed. Artemis broke the flag, and the Goddesses disappeared. Kel stood next to Queen Pallas. &quot;Looks like something is trying to make war inevitable... Ares maybe,&quot; Kel questioned?<br>
<br>
&quot;Perhaps,&quot; Pallas remarked.<br>
<br>
The tribe started a festival to ease Queen Pallas's mind... however, she was worried that someone would be brave enough to go to war with the Goddesses of Olympus. She sat down and watched her tribe dance and be merry. Kel comforted her wife. They decided to wait and see what time would tell.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :| --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/indifferent.gif ALT=":|"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=queenpallas>QueenPallas</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#993300>(8/23/01 4:43 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Queen Pallas Restores Order...</span><hr size=1> After the nightly Saurian attack, Queen Pallas ordered the Amazons of the Sacred Circle to restore order. She sent Phyphen, one of her comrads to fetch new horses for the tribe. By nightfall again, the nation was restored. <br>
<br>
Queen Pallas built a fire and sat down next to her tribe. They all began to talk of times when Harmonia, the Great Amazon Mother, once had a hand in Amazon affairs. Kel laughed at Pallas as she talked of the stories of the Great Ancient Amazons... especially Hippolyte, who fought, so that their sisters would not have to...Kel and the others enjoyed their night together, then retired until the next day break. <br>
<br>
The Goddesses of Olympus kept careful watch over the Sacred group of Amazons... Let no Human, Creature, or Beast dare challenge the Olympian Goddesses....  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm30.showPrevMessage?topicID=14.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm30.showNextMessage?topicID=14.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm30.emailToFriend?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm30.threadControl?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm30.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm30.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsunitefrm39">G